Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:03.23,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,接下来请本人说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 我差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:09.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:10.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 有那么疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:13.76,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:15.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站得起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:16.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来站站看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:19.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,中富同学你的脸原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 我是玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叫我玲实就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 好像是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,正式名称是零分玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.35,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,中富同学你被吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:37.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不会吃你的啦
