Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.52,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,各位都是东吾野的居民吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.86,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(945,762)\an7\fs90\bord0.6\pos(86.666,172)}第3话   短暂 快乐又轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.63,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.14,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,这是电车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对 是电车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.31,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,已经好久没看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.70,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,各位是从哪来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,隔壁的吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:29.57,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}吾野吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.06,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}她说是吾野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.41,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}吾野啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.92,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}吾野吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.78,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,这可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.95,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,现在可以说是远道而来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.71,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,肯定很不容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.51,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,吾野的人们还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,精神…是挺精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:49.81,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,请务必在本处培养…不 静养 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:54.07,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,幸好东吾野的人口在减少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.92,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,所以空房子有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 帮大忙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:57.98,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,请务必
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.72,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.24,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我们没多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.45,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,这种事情请不要操心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.42,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.42,Default,Group,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这里人都给人很好的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,和吾野大不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.99,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野都是食肉 食草动物针锋相对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,夏日祭都不得不终止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.51,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 是因为在争神社供品应该用什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我觉得哪个都可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:32.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,明明用吾野的特产 大米 苦瓜和中麦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.76,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,苦瓜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难道松田小姐你讨厌苦瓜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.94,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,啊 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.23,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,倒不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,再说苦瓜感觉比西葫芦或红辣椒土得多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我倒是挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们这样没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟要去池袋那样的大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,现在哪知道以后会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}松田小姐你去过池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:04.67,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,我以前住在那里 但是现在搬回东吾野了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,比这里更都市化吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.28,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.61,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,我认为确实是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.21,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.30,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,我现在已经没兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你之前见过这个女生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在池袋那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.47,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然…是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.36,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,好 完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,刘海这样可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.11,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真是的 好好看下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香你觉得好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来合影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是刘海纪念！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.80,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶～有模有样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:51.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.08,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.48,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,在东吾野 我们认为顾客至上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.04,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,特别推荐雾气桑拿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.41,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,与其说是推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.97,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,不如说请务必
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.73,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,请务必去体验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.72,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,那稍后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们是不是身上有汗臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说桑拿到底在哪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.87,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶～看上去好时髦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呜哇！好大的雾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不错啊！进去吧进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉可以解毒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,趁这个机会把衣服洗了晾干吧 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,一个人先不说 和大家一起就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,在我们面前脱衣服感觉很害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.97,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明明没必要在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.33,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,总之我就不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,从吾野跑出来真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是我又不可能一个人留在吾野…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.11,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.55,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,我想你们蒸桑拿后大概会觉得饿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.01,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.23,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,你不喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊不会 没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.30,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.43,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,杂煮饭很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.25,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,毕竟是松口蘑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.94,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,你蒸雾气桑拿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.23,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 是的 差不多吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是其他人蒸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.23,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.84,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,今晚请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.04,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,好 好 休 息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:45.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这是什么啊 晶 美味佳肴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,刚刚松田小姐送过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是周到啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.38,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,做了桑拿之后肚子都饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要吃猪肉包金针菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:11.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不觉得奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哪里奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这里的人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,他们不是很亲切吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然头上长着蘑菇就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就是这点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么他们长着蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,去问问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.13,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不行啊这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:21.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就跟不能问戴假发的人 头上是不是假发一个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,礼仪 礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不就是蘑菇嘛 有什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野的人都是动物哦 动物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里的人也不会成天「肉 肉」地叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:36.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很友善嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,东吾野真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,太缺心眼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喂 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这个零分玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不过是厕所 我一个人也能上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:16.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么桑拿房一下子就能看见 厕所却那么远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,设计得很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.63,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,等不及了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.11,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,新人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.60,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,果然外地的都很蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.98,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,什么都没怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.43,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,我们说什么他们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.67,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,一鼓作气地拿下她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.44,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,让她们成为我们的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.49,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,这也是为了她们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.38,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,我们只是在帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.01,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:21.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松田小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:35.42,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,因为还不适应 所以梦见了什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是的 别再打扰别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶 对松田小姐道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.26,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说「大声打扰到你们我很抱歉」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.85,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.69,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,请好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再回去睡一觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这里 总觉得很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,快点离开这里吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你可真是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是因为害怕了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,玲实你和她一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 才不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.15,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶的睡相很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们去厕所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你还要去的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.79,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你别走哦 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看不到星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明天也是阴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,被骗了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.23,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,阴谋论吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你真喜欢共鸡会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是共济会！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们马上就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一晚就长成这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是不是日照太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.53,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,才不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,一直是雾天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,缠得真结实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.87,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,枝叶长得到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 已经成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说是这个苦味才是营养来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们怎么像吓了一大跳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:04.64,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,说到底阳光直射对所有生物都不好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.70,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,热和干燥会导致枯萎 这是宇宙的法则！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:14.24,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,然而 这样还能茁壮成长 开花结果是异常的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:17.11,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,就是因为有这些渴求高温和光照的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.07,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,世界才变得这么奇怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:24.38,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,总之请把那些苦…全都薅下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.76,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们本来就是这么打算的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.05,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她这么讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总之 先把这些全薅下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不会是阴谋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,阴谋？什么样的？是谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为了让我们没法出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你又在说怪话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不奇怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你和我一起负责讨伐苦瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这段时间 玲实和抚子就去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,存一些保质期久的食物比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,太危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有许多需要担心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.66,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,东吾野会有便利店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,拜托你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静…玲…抚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.69,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你在想些什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不行！不行的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那边就拜托你了 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们不是要去池袋吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你的雄心壮志去哪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我根本就不能理解为什么你们能这么安心！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我去看看她们俩！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实！抚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}她说可以免费送给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.85,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.16,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们已经不再需要这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:02.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「不再」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.59,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,我 我是说你们更需要这些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你真是太亲切啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.33,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有了这些 我们就暂时不用担心物资的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就算你这么亲切地对待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们也不会给你任何回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,毕竟我们很快就要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不像吾野 东吾野的人比较体贴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.44,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且很温和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,洋溢着博爱的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,才没有这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:31.44,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,东吾野曾经也有许多人 内心充斥着不满和担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.36,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,但是呀 在7G事件之后 我们终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.03,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,相比痛苦地苟延残喘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.32,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,享受短暂而充实的时间 这种生活方式更好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.72,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,自从我们决定这样子活下去以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.62,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,就再也没有任何事情能让我们生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真深奥啊 松田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.88,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们也能拥有这样的心境吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.92,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.36,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,你们也很快就会变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们快出发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留还在担心我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.78,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,担心？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是真能变成松田小姐那样就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不行！我们可是要去池袋的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.64,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么？池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就待在东吾野不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好像也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不行的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们还得去见叶香呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.49,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你这不是没剪苦瓜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 苦瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:31.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在想 做这些事情真的有意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们真的能到池袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我开始觉得我们到不了池袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.03,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.87,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们不是昨天才出发的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就算到了 也无法改变任何事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是要去找叶香吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就算我们与叶香重逢 说不定也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不如说 也许她根本不想见我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你不去见她怎么能知道呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实和抚子也说点什么吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶 你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.12,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起凄惨地挣扎求存
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不如过上短暂 快乐又轻松的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的就是现在的这种心理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.49,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不行了 全完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,五点了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这里是晶 现在位于东吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.93,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,这里是吾野 请汇报状况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,很多蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.87,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,到处都是蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,告诉我蘑菇的危险度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.71,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,什么？蘑菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.40,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.25,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,要香味找松口蘑 要口味找丛生口蘑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.55,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,用狗而非猪去寻找松露？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.87,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,白胜于黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:44.51,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,说起来 蘑菇有时会像画圈一样长成环状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.63,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,虽然人们自古以来便认为这是妖精或是魔女的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.30,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,实际上 这是伴随着菌类的生长与死亡而呈现的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.98,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,也有人认为蘑菇圈会出现在落雷之后 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我才不关心什么雷的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,该如何躲避和逃离蘑菇？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇喜欢阴暗潮湿帽帽帽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,帽帽帽帽帽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.29,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这宝贵的五分钟都浪费在 无聊的蘑菇趣闻上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:21.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,苦瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.58,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,为什么要反抗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.60,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,明明只要加入我们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.14,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,像你现在这样活着又有什么好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,变成蘑菇才会有坏处啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.83,Default,King Oyster,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.26,Default,King Oyster,0,0,0,,蘑菇没有烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.80,Default,Enoki,0,0,0,,蘑菇不会痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.64,Default,Fly Agaric,0,0,0,,蘑菇不需要思考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.36,Default,Group,0,0,0,,大家一起变成蘑菇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,绝对不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.15,Default,Resident,0,0,0,,会很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇军团！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.70,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我想过平和的生活呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:08.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么都不必思考 身体轻飘飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.66,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,别发呆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你们之前说去池袋的 豪言壮语都到哪去了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是要去池袋赶时髦吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,时髦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是要去见叶香吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.79,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么能呆在这种地方长蘑菇呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:35.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香这家伙 擅自离开吾野 擅自消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,她不是我们的朋友吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她以前是我的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从她离开的那时候起 就已经不是朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:52.71,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说到底 我对叶香的想法根本一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留 努力学习才对你有好处呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？我就算吃亏也无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:04.40,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你还没有提交规划调查表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,规划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.53,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,没有想做的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想变得特别聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:12.02,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,那样的话要好好学习了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,又是学习啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香 你有规划吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:17.73,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,有的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是什么？什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.50,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我想去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别糊弄过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那种地方坐电车一下子就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也许我应该凭借我的吾野柔术成为一名综合格斗家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.59,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,吾野柔术擅长打击\N因此可能适合综合格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想和食蚁兽打一架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.82,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.93,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是认真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:35.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.00,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们要去池袋 去见叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:43.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去池袋 和叶香见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.10,Default,Shiitake,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.40,Default,Enoki,0,0,0,,你要放弃这份安宁吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.43,Default,Shimeji,0,0,0,,别当叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:59.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,轻松地活下去与否 由我自己来决定！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:06.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,玩笑玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只是个小玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哇啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们去把抚子和玲实的蘑菇拔下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:15.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.38,Default,King Oyster,0,0,0,,你知道你有多幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.15,Default,Porcini,0,0,0,,{\an8}保护新的同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.18,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不要擅自把别人当成同伴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.85,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我在做什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.53,Default,Group,0,0,0,,蘑菇！蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大家的意识都被蘑菇夺取了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.66,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,被这么包围着就是跑也跑不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或许…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的就拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦！瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.67,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,不要！求你了别！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,被蘑菇寄生操纵着就接受了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.91,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,不要…我警告过你不要了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:05.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松田小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.56,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,什么嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.90,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.75,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,别来管我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.76,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,明明特意对你们亲切的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,亲切？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.05,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,我们是自愿被蘑菇寄生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:20.45,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,相比在这该死的没有未来的世界里再过个几十年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.22,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,长出蘑菇就能 快乐嬉皮家里蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.16,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,过一两年就死掉 绝对更好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,过一两年就死掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.43,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,去池袋有什么意义嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.28,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我有一个想见的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.80,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,见到了又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.15,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,再说了绝对见不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是果然我还是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不去确认一下的话我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.68,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,是不是傻啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:48.30,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,你们就尽情地挣扎 最后吐血而死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.63,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,再也不管你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.60,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,哼 随你们便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.50,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,蘑菇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是一种什么感觉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.08,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你刚才也长出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子你不也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果蘑菇再长大一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说不定就会觉得就这样死去也不错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,确实可能是一种不错的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,轻飘飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,该说是不可思议呢还是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,话说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,大家都应该感谢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:49.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感谢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.31,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我救了你们啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好 好 感谢感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,太随便了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喂等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,连狗都来捉弄我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么都没有！
